          </tr>
          <tr class="luxury-row">
            <td><div class="repair-type">Sub-Zero / luxury built-in <span class="luxury-badge">LUXURY</span></div><div class="repair-desc">All failure types</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$320&ndash;$910+</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ OEM parts (premium pricing)</div></td>
            <td>Proprietary components, sealed systems, custom panel integration, limited access clearance</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="luxury-row">
