    <p class="table-note"><strong>All prices are labor only.</strong> After diagnosis we quote the specific part needed as a separate line item &mdash; you see the OEM part cost before approving anything. Quote before we start; invoice matches the quote. 90-day warranty on parts and labor.</p>
